snippet.title: Gears of War: Judgment VGA 2012 trailer
snippet.description:
Developed exclusively for Xbox 360 by Epic Games and People Can Fly, Gears of War: Judgment launches in the UK on 22nd March 2013.

This is the "World Premiere" trailer as screened on Spike TV during its Video Games Awards 2012.
